    <briefdescription>
<para>This block prints data of messages filled with data of the structure [ [[symbol_0],[data_0]], [[symbol_1],[data_1]], ...] on the command line. Only data of the datatypes f32vector and long, and rx_time tuples are displayed. The output can also be stored in a text file. </para>
    </briefdescription>
